pointwise operations and checking that they are compatible with the uniform distance. -/
variable [TopologicalSpace Œ±] [SemiNormedGroup Œ≤]

variable (f g : Œ± ‚Üí·µá Œ≤) {x : Œ±} {C : ‚Ñù}

