  ‚ü®fun f => (ofNormedGroup (-f) f.Continuous.neg ‚à•f‚à•) fun x => trans_rel_right _ (norm_neg _) (f.norm_coe_le_norm x)‚ü©

/-- The pointwise difference of two bounded continuous functions is again bounded continuous. -/
