  ‚ü®fun f : Œ± ‚Üí·µá ùïú g : Œ± ‚Üí·µá Œ≤ =>
    ofNormedGroup (fun x => f x ‚Ä¢ g x) (f.Continuous.smul g.Continuous) (‚à•f‚à• * ‚à•g‚à•) fun x =>
      calc
